<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6958232>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. A–C. Myolepta petiolata Thompson, 1971, ♀ (ZFMK-DIP-00082511). A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Habitus, dorsal view. C. Head, frontal view. D–F. M. petiolata, ♀, holotype (BPBM). D. Habitus, lateral view. E. Habitus, dorsal view. F. Habitus, frontal view. Scale bars: A–B =1 mm; C= 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6958232/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6958226>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Myolepta geras sp. nov., ♂, holotype (ZFMK-DIP-00082513). A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Habitus, dorsal view. C. Head, frontal view. D. Genitalia, hypandrium, lateral view. E. Genitalia, epandrium, lateral view. F. Genitalia, epandrium, dorsoposterior view. G. Genitalia, epandrium, ventral view. H. Genitalia, hypandrium, dorsal view. I. Genitalia, hypandrium, ventral view. Scale bars: A–C=1 mm; D–I =0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6958226/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6958220>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Myolepta graciliventris Wiegmann, 1986, ♂, holotype (USNMENT01754756). A. Habitus, dorsal view. B. Habitus, lateral view. C. Head, frontal view. D. Labels. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6958220/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6958222>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. A–C. Myolepta diaphora sp. nov., ♀, holotype (ZFMK-DIP-00082516). A. Habitus, lateral view. B. Habitus, dorsal view. C. Head, frontal view. D–F. M. orientalis Thompson, 1971, ♀, holotype (BPBM). D. Habitus, lateral view. E. Habitus, dorsal view. F. Head, frontal view. Scale bars: A–C= 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6958222/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6958230>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Myolepta iota sp. nov., ♂, holotype (ZFMK-DIP-00082514). A. Habitus, lateral view.B. Habitus, dorsal view. C. Head, frontal view. D. Genitalia, hypandrium, lateral view. E. Genitalia, epandrium, lateral view. F. Genitalia, epandrium, dorsoposterior view. G. Genitalia, epandrium, ventral view. H. Genitalia, hypandrium, dorsal view. I. Genitalia, hypandrium, ventral view. Scale bars: A–B =1 mm; C=0.5 mm; D–I =0.1 mm." ;
